# Demo's gen/ is the buf-generated proto Go module + Python bindings. We
# commit these so `git clone && cd examples/demo && go build ./...` works
# without the buf+protoc toolchain. `.gitattributes` marks them as
# linguist-generated so GitHub collapses them from PR diffs.
